From: FreshChromatic <noreply@freshchromatic.com>
Date: Sun, 26 Apr 2026 16:22:02 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Add Folia async support via PlatformScheduler

Migrate all Bukkit scheduler APIs to PlatformScheduler abstraction layer
to support Folia's region-threaded scheduler model.

Co-Authored-By: FreshChromatic <noreply@freshchromatic.com>
